
description:
This ruby script is for auto testing using vow with specified interval.
The result can be found in "auto-vows.log".

usage:
auto_vows INTERVAL(sec) testfile

examples
In following example, "vows foo-test.js and vows bar-test.js" should be executed every five seconds.
$ ruby auto_vows 5 foo-test.js bar-test.js
$ more auto-vows.log
